      "content": "i tried one of my allergy pills like 20 mins ago but it doesnt really seem to be doing much. the whistling is getting kinda louder tho. do u think it's worth waiting another hour to see if the antihistamine kicks in or should i be worried about something else? i dont really want to go to a doctor if i can just sleep it off.",
